criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 18;

          -  Patients who have undergone hematopoietic stem cell transplantation (HSCT);

          -  Patients who don't take any drug including Eltrombopag and rhTPO before hematopoietic
             stem cell transplantation (HSCT);

          -  Patients receiving either an autologous (Auto) or allogeneic (Allo) stem cell
             transplantation from a sibling,related donor, or matched unrelated donor are included;

          -  Agree to sign informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with thrombocytopenia causes by other reasons, such as drugs, cytomegalovirus
             or infection;

          -  Patients who had greater risk of thromboembolic disease within six months;

          -  Patients with a history of heart disease;

          -  Patients with severe organ dysfunction;

          -  Patients with other malignancies
